                          Our Solutions

                          As education evolves, Edmentum is poised to offer best-in-class solutions to your current challenges. We offer award-winning, K–12 curricula, assessments, and instructional services to meet your program goals.

                          • Build programs to boost graduation and postsecondary success
                          • Offer individualized options to accelerate growth and achievement gains
                          • Initiate blended, virtual, or summer solutions to meet unique needs

                          Solutions that meet your needs

                          We go beyond providing the latest learning technology. Edmentum partners with you to solve problems, address challenges, and make your goals for student learning achievable.

                          Career Connected Learning

                          Students face a rapidly evolving job market requiring different skills, education, and experience. Our career and technical learning (CTE) programs keep students engaged in school while preparing them for the workplace.

                          Digital curricula unlock equitable pathways for first-time credit and credit recovery. Edmentum provides courses, intervention, and blended learning solutions in a single platform to reach graduation goals—and beyond.

                          Programs built on research to drive impact

                          Learn how rigorous and ongoing research, third-party validations, and success stories from our partners confirm the effectiveness and quality of our solutions.

                          ESSA Tier 2 Research
                          Saved by the Bell: The Effects of Digital Curricula on Student Attendance, Punctuality, and Academic Performance

                          Students who successfully completed at least one Courseware course demonstrated higher rates of attendance and punctuality, and higher average grades by the end of the semester.

                          ESSA Tier 2 Research
                          Courseware Algebra 1 Students Score Significantly Higher on NWEA® MAP® Growth™ Assessments

                          Learning accelerated on NWEA MAP Growth assessments for 9th grade students enrolled in Courseware Algebra 1 and English 1.

                          ESSA Tier 2 Research
                          Success for Diverse Learners on Renaissance Star® Math Assessments with Exact Path

                          The use of Exact Path was positively related to math achievement as measured by the Renaissance Star Math assessments.

                          ESSA Tier 2 Research
                          Sizable Increase in NWEA® MAP® Growth™ Math and Reading Scores in First Year of Exact Path Implementation

                          First year implementation of Exact Path leads to growth in NWEA® MAP® math and reading scores.
